---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout-Kinniku.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import KinnikufesHeaderImage from "../images/kinnikufes__header-image.webp";
import KinnikufesMainImage from "../images/kinnikufes__main-image.webp";
---

<Layout title="筋肉のフェスティバル | あじがさわフードフェス2024">
  <header class="header">
    <div class="header__container">
      <section class="header__image">
        <Image src={KinnikufesHeaderImage} alt="筋肉フェスタイトル" />
      </section>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main class="main">
    <div class="main__container">
      <p class="heading07" data-en="About">
        あじがさわ筋肉のフェスティバルとは
      </p>
      <section class="main__text">
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Event">開催日時</h2>
          <p>2024年10月8日（SUN）</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Hours">受付時間</h2>
          <p>9:00～9:30 <br />（当日のエントリーは出来ません）</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Place">受付場所</h2>
          <p>鰺ヶ沢町中央公民館 2階</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Venue">会場</h2>
          <p>鰺ヶ沢町 海の駅わんど向かい特設会場</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Class">クラス</h2>
          <p>男性フリー、女性フリー（年齢・身長・体重等全てフリー）</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Cost">参加費</h2>
          <p>無料</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Period">申込期間</h2>
          <p>2024年8月1日（木）～9月17日（火）</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="heading06" data-en="Apply">応募方法</h2>
          <p>
            <a
              href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfC-YOdrZZrBvcpoyb4g99i8TxxJhqLw5IeVJ0vt8iY_NJ-lg/viewform?usp=sf_link"
              target="_blank">専用フォームからお申込みください</a
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <div class="blog-card">
        <div class="meta">
          <div
            class="photo"
            style="background-image: url(/images/card-bg01.webp)"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <h1>パフォーマンス</h1>
          <h2>performance</h2>
          <p>
            受付終了後、パーソナルジムCORE　木村拓磨
            氏による演技指導を（30分程度）行い、本番の審査では下記内容にて審査を行います。
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              グループ審査&nbsp;フロント（2ポーズ）&nbsp;15秒、バック（2ポーズ）&nbsp;15秒
            </li>
            <li>一人ずつ&nbsp;フリーポーズ&nbsp;20秒</li>
            <li>
              審査員アピール&nbsp;審査員から呼ばれた選手&nbsp;フロント・バック各２ポーズ&nbsp;30秒
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card alt">
        <div class="meta">
          <div
            class="photo"
            style="background-image: url(/images/card-bg02.webp)"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <h1>審査員</h1>
          <h2>Judge</h2>
          <p>５名</p>
          <p>特別審査員　パーソナルジムＣＯＲＥ　オーナー　木村　拓磨 氏</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card">
        <div class="meta">
          <div
            class="photo"
            style="background-image: url(/images/card-bg03.webp)"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <h1>審査基準</h1>
          <h2>Judging criteria</h2>
          <p></p>
          <ul>
            <li>全体のバランス</li>
            <li>筋肉の発達</li>
            <li>ポーズ</li>
            <li>表情</li>
            <li>ユーモア</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card alt">
        <div class="meta">
          <div
            class="photo"
            style="background-image: url(/images/card-bg04.webp)"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <h1>服装規定</h1>
          <h2>Dress Code</h2>
          <p></p>
          <ul>
            <li>男性：腰から膝までのハーフパンツ等</li>
            <li>女性：スポーツブラ、ショートパンツ</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card">
        <div class="meta">
          <div
            class="photo"
            style="background-image: url(/images/card-bg05.webp)"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <h1>大会賞品</h1>
          <h2>competition prizes</h2>
          <p></p>
          <ul>
            <li>優勝者　パーソナルジムCORE　プロテイン</li>
            <li>特別審査員賞　パーソナルジムCORE　トレーニングチケット</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="blog-card alt">
        <div class="meta">
          <div
            class="photo"
            style="background-image: url(/images/card-bg06.webp)"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <h1>注意事項</h1>
          <h2>competition prizes</h2>
          <p></p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              タトゥー等ある方は、ファンデーション、シール等で隠せる範囲で出場可能です。
            </li>
            <li>ボディメイクを始めたばかりの方も参加可能です。</li>
            <li>当日の飛び入り参加はできません。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="main__image">
        <Image src={KinnikufesMainImage} alt="特別審査員" />
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer__container">
    <div class="footer__main">
      <div>
        <p>主催</p>
        <p>鰺ヶ沢</p>
        <p>協力</p>
        <p>鰺ヶ沢町観光協会、鯵ヶ沢町商工会、パーソナルジムCORE</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>お問い合わせ先</p>
        <p>
          あじがさわフードフェス2024開催業務受託　株式会社プラス　五所川原市字田町121番地2<br
          />TEL 0173-26-7071（平日9：00～17：00）／FAX 0173-26-7072
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style lang="scss">
  $color_white: #fff;
  $color_prime: rgba(225, 255, 0, 01);
  $color_grey: #e2e2e2;
  $color_grey_dark: #a2a2a2;
  html {
    background-color: #120811;
    color: #120811;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN",
      "Hiragino Sans", Meiryo, sans-serif;
  }

  a {
    text-decoration: none;
    &:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  }

  /* header */
  .header {
    background-image: url("../images/kinnikufes__header-background.webp");
    background-size: cover;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: bottom -500px right 0px;
    backdrop-filter: brightness(60%);
  }

  .header__container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header__image {
    & img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* main */
  .main {
    background-color: #120811;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 0 1.5rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }

  .main__container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #120811;
  }

  .main__header {
    & p {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      position: relative;
      padding: 0.1em 0.5em;
      font-weight: bold;

      background: linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        #f4db24 0%,
        #f29115 45%,
        #f4db24 70%,
        #f29115 85%,
        #f4db24 90% 100%
      );
      color: #120811;
    }
  }

  .main__header-item {
    & ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0 0 0 1rem;
      & li {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    }
  }

  .main__image {
    width: 100%;
    & img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
  }

  .main__text {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-between;
    & div {
      width: 50%;
      & p {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #fff;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* footer */
  .footer__main {
    padding: 0 1.5rem 0 1.5rem;
    border-top: solid 5px #120811;
    & div:nth-of-type(1) {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      & p {
        padding: 2px 8px;
      }
      & p:nth-of-type(1) {
        border: solid 2px #120811;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }

      & p:nth-of-type(3) {
        border: solid 2px #120811;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    }
    & div:nth-of-type(2) {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      & p {
        padding: 2px 8px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }
      & p:nth-of-type(1) {
        border: solid 2px #120811;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      border-top: solid 1px #120811;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      & div {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
        & p {
          padding: 0;
        }
      }
      & div:nth-of-type(2) {
        gap: 0;
      }
      & div:nth-of-type(1) {
        gap: 0;
      }
    }
  }

  .footer__container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .blog-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin: 1rem auto;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 7px -1px rgba(#000, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 1.6%;
    background: $color_white;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-family: sans-serif;
    border-radius: 5px;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 0;
    a {
      color: inherit;
      &:hover {
        color: $color_prime;
      }
    }
    &:hover {
      .photo {
        transform: scale(1.3) rotate(3deg);
      }
    }
    .meta {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 0;
      height: 200px;
    }
    .photo {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .details,
    .details ul {
      margin: auto;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .details {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      left: -100%;
      margin: auto;
      transition: left 0.2s;
      background: rgba(#000, 0.6);
      color: $color_white;
      padding: 10px;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      a {
        text-decoration: dotted underline;
      }
      ul li {
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .author:before {
        font-family: FontAwesome;
        margin-right: 10px;
        content: "\f007";
      }

      .date:before {
        font-family: FontAwesome;
        margin-right: 10px;
        content: "\f133";
      }

      .tags {
        ul:before {
          font-family: FontAwesome;
          content: "\f02b";
          margin-right: 10px;
        }
        li {
          margin-right: 2px;
          &:first-child {
            margin-left: -4px;
          }
        }
      }
    }
    .description {
      padding: 3rem;
      background: $color_white;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      height: 245px;
      h1,
      h2 {
        font-family: Poppins, sans-serif;
      }
      h1 {
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.7rem;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: $color_grey_dark;
        margin-top: 5px;
        font-family: luxus-brut, cursive;
      }
      .read-more {
        text-align: right;
        a {
          color: $color_prime;
          display: inline-block;
          position: relative;
          &:after {
            content: "\f061";
            font-family: FontAwesome;
            margin-left: -10px;
            opacity: 0;
            vertical-align: middle;
            transition:
              margin 0.3s,
              opacity 0.3s;
          }

          &:hover:after {
            margin-left: 5px;
            opacity: 1;
          }
        }
      }
    }
    p {
      position: relative;
      margin: 1rem 0 0;
      &:first-of-type {
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
        &:before {
          content: "";
          position: absolute;
          height: 5px;
          background: $color_prime;
          width: 35px;
          top: -0.75rem;
          border-radius: 3px;
        }
      }
    }
    &:hover {
      .details {
        left: 0%;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 640px) {
      flex-direction: row;

      .meta {
        flex-basis: 40%;
        height: auto;
      }
      .description {
        flex-basis: 60%;
        &:before {
          transform: skewX(-3deg);
          content: "";
          background: #fff;
          width: 30px;
          position: absolute;
          left: -10px;
          top: 0;
          bottom: 0;
          z-index: -1;
        }
      }
      &.alt {
        flex-direction: row-reverse;
        .description {
          &:before {
            left: inherit;
            right: -10px;
            transform: skew(3deg);
          }
        }
        .details {
          padding-left: 25px;
        }
      }
    }
  }
  .heading06 {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 50px;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .heading06 span {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .heading06::before {
    content: attr(data-en);
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(225, 255, 0, 0.5);
    font-size: 50px;
    font-family: luxus-brut, cursive;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .heading07 {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 50px;
    padding-left: 30px;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .heading07 span {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .heading07::before {
    content: attr(data-en);
    position: absolute;
    transform: rotate(-5deg);
    top: -20px;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(225, 255, 0, 0.5);
    font-size: 80px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-family: luxus-brut, cursive;
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
